{"tid":1390782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再拎錢拎物資拎現券出黎","createTime":"2019-07-31T08:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T10:12:07.000Z","uid":58676,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39438149d20fdb471f1909630f91924c1ef9e607","tid":1390782,"uid":58676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:34:13.000Z","msg":"感謝大家一片好心，資助各位義士<br />\n但係其實佢地除左物資同gear<br />\n最需要既係人<br />\n係希望更多人一齊上前線<br />\n前線人多先可以佈陣<br />\n先可以有更多戰術<br />\n<br />\n前線人多夠勇武<br />\n催淚彈打散前排 就後排有人補上<br />\n可以一齊圍嘔落單狗隊<br />\n可以互相分工輪更 養精蓄銳<br />\n<br />\n我講多一次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>前線要人<br />\n前線要人<br />\n前線要人</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n不喜勿插"},{"pid":"c147d038fe6b85f0c949126fa1f0510e1a0e45a5","tid":1390782,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:34:52.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"0384fc772c0dd17ad25d82b6d73eee66de741b60","tid":1390782,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:35:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc54c3fe7d5e7721eb35a81593716e2d53abf25d","tid":1390782,"uid":58676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:02:09.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"80acac6c618700d58e0008a5f98c31814713387e","tid":1390782,"uid":58676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"05c9abf1f8741b70e00a2313db414c03915713ed","tid":1390782,"uid":58676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:03:03.000Z","msg":"要求釋放所有義士"},{"pid":"55699422bfbfa2a9d47a466e47bfb387104b6b84","tid":1390782,"uid":58676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:03:17.000Z","msg":"八五罷工全面癱瘓"},{"pid":"c662be72d2f04afafee2802611c2c64c47ecc0ba","tid":1390782,"uid":58676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:03:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"37